2. Select your **Windows ISO**
3. Choose partition size (Windows side)
4. Click **Install**
5. Mac restarts â†’ Windows installer opens
6. Select **BOOTCAMP** partition
7. Complete Windows setup
8. Install Boot Camp drivers when prompted

---

## ðŸ”„ Switching Between macOS & Windows
- Restart and hold **Option (âŒ¥)** key
- Choose macOS or Windows

